t=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/4d5d96e0ddc077b5d6bda7dd21343329.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An official screenshot of flame magic in use in Path of Exile 2.\" data-chomp-id=\"4d5d96e0ddc077b5d6bda7dd21343329\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"An official screenshot of flame magic in use in Path of Exile 2.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/4d5d96e0ddc077b5d6bda7dd21343329.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Grinding Gear Games\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"4d5d96e0ddc077b5d6bda7dd21343329\" data-recommend-id=\"image://4d5d96e0ddc077b5d6bda7dd21343329\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An official screenshot of flame magic in use in Path of Exile 2.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith every passing level and zone in \u003cem\u003ePath of Exile 2\u003c/em\u003e, you’ll find yourself following one of two paths: Either you’re gaining strength and clearing zones with ease, or you’re struggling to beat a boss and require the help of someone else in global chat. You want to be on the former path, leading you to unlock your Ascendancies in \u003cem\u003ePath of Exile 2.\u003c/em\u003e Ascendancies are entirely new and highly specialized classes that evolve your base character to new and greater heights.  - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/path-of-exile-2-ascendancy-classes-switch-change-unlock-1851759862\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/path-of-exile-2-ascendancy-classes-switch-change-unlock-1851759862\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003