 of the character selection screen shows Hulk making an aggressive gesture.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A screenshot of the character selection screen shows Hulk making an aggressive gesture.\" data-chomp-id=\"817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1078\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of the character selection screen shows Hulk making an aggressive gesture.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Marvel Games / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b\" data-recommend-id=\"image://817f805700c9a2d3315935c03a196b1b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1078\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A screenshot of the character selection screen shows Hulk making an aggressive gesture.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eVanguards are \u003cem\u003eMarvel Rivals\u003c/em\u003e’ version of Tanks, the characters that distract the enemy and soak the damage so your softer, more high-damage-dealing characters can focus on what they do best. Every \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-best-vanguard-tank-hulk-thor-strange-1851737184\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-best-vanguard-tank-hulk-thor-strange-1851737184\"\u003eVanguard hero\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e that falls under this classification is a high-HP character that can sufficiently block damage for their team, but they all function differently in terms of play style. A couple have even left some players confused on how to use them. Hulk is one such hero. - Samuel Moreno \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-hulk-how-to-play-vanguard-tank-1851760675\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/marvel-rivals-hulk-how-to-play-vanguard-tank-1851760675\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118\" data-recommend-id=\"image://35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mika stands on a rock with an ocean taking up the background.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mika stands on a rock with an ocean taking up the background.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Mika stands on a rock with an ocean taking up the background.\" data-chomp-id=\"35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Mika stands on a rock with an ocean taking up the background.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Chibig / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118\" data-recommend-id=\"image://35c716092248bbe082b1c991e19d0118\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Mika stands on a rock with an ocean taking up the background.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you’ve been exploring the scenic and cozy Orilla Town in \u003cem\u003eMika and the Witch’s Mountain\u003c/em\u003e, you’ve probably come across a billboard with a piece of paper that says “5505\u0026#34; and asks you to feed five kitties. Feeding cats seems like a humane thing to do, and it’ll be a straightforward affair if you’re using our guide since we’ll tell you where to find all these cute little cats.  - Billy Givens \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/mika-witchs-mountain-kittens-cats-kitties-feed-location-1851759701\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/mika-witchs-mountain-kittens-cats-kitties-feed-location-1851759701\"\u003eR